{"tid":867163,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 爆 RID 綁架漏洞，至少 10 個月未修補","createTime":"2018-10-18T12:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T08:34:51.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c956aa394d2aad1a2459b01bea13ed6abd35dd3f","tid":867163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:18:15.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞安全研究人員發現Windows 上有個很容易執行 RID 綁架漏洞，可讓駭客以他人帳號取得受害電腦的管理員控制權，然而這個存在至少 10 個月的漏洞都未獲得修補<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s4.itho.me/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/rid1.jpg?itok=a-uoHA8P\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.itho.me%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Frid1.jpg%3Fitok%3Da-uoHA8P&h=5a11d51a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n安全公司 CSL 執行長 Pedro Garcia 於去年 12 月發現到這個 RID 綁架（RID hijiacking）漏洞。RID（relative identifier，相對識別碼）是加上用戶帳號安全識別碼（SID）後，描述電腦或網域允許的帳號。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 常見的RID是代表內建管理員帳號的 500 或代表 Guest 的 501<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nGarcia 為測試攻擊撰寫了一個 Metasploit 模組。他發現，只要對 Windows PC 傳送 meterpreter session 即可改寫 Windows 機碼，進而修改和用戶帳號下的 RID，並為另一個帳號群組建立另一組 RID。研究人員表示，雖然這個方法不能引發遠端程式碼執行或感染，但是一旦駭客可藉由惡意程式或暴力破解電腦帳戶密碼，駭客就可以為原本低權限的用戶帳號賦予管理員權限，因而成為 Windows PC 上的後門<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n由於機碼是永久存在的，因此任何竄改在被修復之前都是有效的。此外，本攻擊手法在Windows XP、Server 2003、Windows 8.1和Windows 10系統上都可以試驗成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/126478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F126478&d=lLDkewc10%2F2bRfwr4nLAHBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0601e130\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/126478</a>"},{"pid":"165087b6e6d4ddcd51c8500d7ceff2a896d0e185","tid":867163,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"Garcia 指出，這種手法完全利用 OS 資源，並未引入外部惡意程式，故也不會引發系統警告。只有在檢視登錄檔 ( registry ) 時檢查到安全帳號管理員（security account manager, SAM）有不一致時才可能發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n雖然這對駭客來說是一個天上掉下來的禮物，不過似乎尚未有傳出開採及攻擊行動的消息，但他相信找到該漏洞的不只有他的公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。研究人員對 ZDNet 表示，在發現本項漏洞後已經通知微軟，但並未獲得回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，當然微軟也還未修補漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"56a89be565b0539842cf6f4c8585e61ed665ec99","tid":867163,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskylinux.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskylinux.gif&h=d47d86cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e51ec2b909ceedd7e5341af325ded7e227a6cea","tid":867163,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"win7 冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733e3aa0e43b02f4a6a11257faf91f714e23027d","tid":867163,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T18:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ohw.ooo/husky/huskylinux.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fohw.ooo%2Fhusky%2Fhuskylinux.gif&h=d47d86cd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484c83a845fdf3731afc0c4b65afca62b6ad08db","tid":867163,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"裝linux"}]}